<div class="display-inline-block"><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer text-no-underline bg-transparent border-0 padding-0 text-left margin-0 text-normal text-primary" aria-controls="journal_context_menu">J Am Coll Cardiol</button></div>. Author manuscript; available in PMC: 2011 Aug 24.</div>
<div>
<em>Published in final edited form as: </em>J Am Coll Cardiol. 2010 Jul 9;56(9):702–711. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jacc.2010.05.014" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1016/j.jacc.2010.05.014</a>
